        "酒要多吃饭要饱",
        "闲事闲非不问好",
        "闲来亭园观花草",
        "院子",
        "雄兵百万如山倒",
        "韩当战策全不晓",
        "马孟起斩将赛虎豹",
        "鲁子敬在马上对天祝告",
        "鲁肃",
        "黄忠八十刚强好",
        "黄盖苦肉献粮草"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "乔玄 （内西皮导板） 前三皇后五帝历代有道，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（乔玄上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "夏桀王宠妹喜社稷倾消。\n殷纣王宠妲己苦害群僚。\n姜子牙灭成汤扶保周朝。\n五霸强七雄出累动枪刀。\n传二世楚汉争百姓奔逃。\n四百年至桓灵又起风潮。\n欺天子灭诸侯势压群僚。\n天降下蜀、魏、吴三分汉朝。\n我主爷坐东吴雨顺风调。\n这才是天地人裂土分茅。\n马放山甲入库快乐逍遥。\n文职官也不用费尽心劳。\n享不尽太平福常把香烧。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（院子暗上。四文堂、中军、鲁肃同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾主爷坐东吴治国有道，\n终日里为荆州愁锁眉梢。\n但愿得把荆州讨转回朝。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁子敬在马上对天祝告、中军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此乔相府。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "向前通禀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "门上有人么？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（院子出，问。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "什么人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "鲁大夫求见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "候着！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（院子进内。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启相爷：鲁大夫求见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "说我出迎。回避了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "相爷出迎！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（乔玄出迎。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大夫在哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "太尉！"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大夫！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "乔玄 （同笑） 啊哈哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（鲁肃、乔玄同进门，四文堂、中军、院子同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请坐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "太尉请上，肃大礼参拜！"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大夫少礼。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（鲁肃行礼。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请坐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "告坐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大夫驾到，未曾远迎，当面赎罪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢。来得鲁莽，太尉海涵！"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大夫驾临，有何见谕？"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只为刘备借去我国荆州，久借不还，主公忧闷，此事乃下官作保，心想讨还荆\n州，苦无良策。太尉乃三世元老，必有高见。特来求一妙计，讨回荆州，望乞\n指示。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听大夫之言，要讨取荆州么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "依老朽之见，荆州不讨也罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "若不讨回，岂不失了主公的锐气。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你可记得赤壁鏖兵多亏何人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "令婿周郎。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "非也，多亏孔明先生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎见得？"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "曾记得曹瞒打战表，\n要把东吴一笔消。\n吓坏了东吴众群僚。\n武将不敢动枪刀。\n东吴早已降了曹。\n凤雏连环巧计高。\n怎能够赤壁把兵鏖。\n百万儿郎水上飘。\n情理二字一旦抛。\n何必累次把心焦。\n免得军民受煎熬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "雄兵百万如山倒、文官准备写降表、不是孔明计策好、黄盖苦肉献粮草、不是孔明暗地保、只烧得战船都沉了、到如今太平无事好、荆州不过弹丸地、劝大夫休把荆州讨、鲁肃",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "太尉说话言不妙，\n长他志气灭吾朝。\n吴侯也曾费辛劳。\n武将何曾解战袍。\n不讨荆州留祸苗。\n岂肯与他两开交。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔明破曹计虽好、文官昼夜忙不了、渔人取利令人恼、借荆州本是下官保、乔玄",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "休要提起你作保，\n大夫做事也不高。\n何曾讨转半分毫。\n我婿周郎带箭逃。\n吴太后弄假成真、在甘露寺内把亲招。\n中了孔明计笼牢。\n贯甲将军血染袍。\n我婿周郎一命抛。"
        },
        {
          "character": "三翻四次把荆州讨、一取荆州损粮草、二取荆州美人计、三取荆州更不妙、只杀得人头马后掉、损兵折将还事小、鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "提起令婿周郎命丧巴丘，还是下官搬尸回来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可还记得路过哪些险要？"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "云蒙山。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大夫，你只知搬尸回来，可记得你那丢脸现丑的日子？"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "年深日久，下官忘怀了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "曾记得大夫搬尸回来，路过云蒙山，在那宜阳江中，现出一员大将，头戴乌油\n盔，身穿乌油甲，手执丈八矛，大吼一声：“呔！东吴搬尸的是谁？”只吓得\n大夫战战兢兢，躬身答道：我乃东吴鲁——"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（乔玄作身段。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一个“鲁”字未曾出口，你就掉在那船舱之中。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那是下官靴大失足。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "说什么靴大失足，分明被那张飞吓掉了你的三魂。那时节幸喜掉在那船舱里面，\n若是掉在宜阳江中，那些江水，你一时怎能喝得干哪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大吼一声如雷啸，\n你战战兢兢跌一跤。\n身上斜穿紫罗袍。\n阎王面前走一遭。\n张翼德才饶了你的命一条！\n大夫一命赴阴曹！\n提防张飞丈八矛。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吓得你歪戴乌纱帽、三魂七魄都失了、再三再四苦哀告、若不是素日之间孙、刘两家的情义好、你若要把荆州讨、鲁肃",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "太尉休得来取笑，\n从前事儿一旦抛。\n不敢与我国动枪刀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备、孔明兵将少、乔玄",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你道刘备人马少，\n他有五虎将英豪：\n百步穿杨箭法高。\n在渭水杀曹操割须又弃袍。\n在长坂坡前称英豪。\n千里独行胆量高。\n一声喝断当阳桥。\n挡住西川路一条。\n一个个杀气森森广略韬。\n我东吴哪一个比他高？"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠八十刚强好、马孟起斩将赛虎豹、赵子龙生来胆不小、关羽春秋韬略好、张翼德大吼如雷啸、严颜八十不为老、五虎上将比不了、想想西蜀众将校、鲁肃",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "太尉说话年迈了，\n忘了我国将英豪：\n凌统、甘宁是英豪。\n程普、潘璋志亮高。\n韩当、吕蒙将名标。\n只怕那五虎解战袍！"
        },
        {
          "character": "文官阚泽韬略妙、蒋钦、周泰年纪少、丁奉、徐盛武艺好、众将奋勇把荆州讨、乔玄",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你道东吴战将好，\n老朽看来没一条。\n蒋钦、周泰小儿曹。\n程普、潘璋是毛包。\n吕蒙粗卤汉一条。\n怕的马仰尸骸抛。\n何必又要动枪刀？\n免得军民受煎熬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "凌统、甘宁无智略、丁奉、徐盛铡马草、韩当战策全不晓、五虎若把东吴到、孙、刘正在结交好、劝你莫把荆州讨、鲁肃",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听罢言来心焦躁，\n怎知吾腹内巧计高。"
        },
        {
          "character": "凌统、甘宁无智略、丁奉、徐盛铡马草、韩当战策全不晓、五虎若把东吴到、孙、刘正在结交好、劝你莫把荆州讨、鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "太尉，刘备倒有还荆州之意，但有一人不允。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何人不允？"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "关羽不允。昨日主公命诸葛瑾过江求亲，关羽口出不逊之言。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "什么不逊之言？"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他说：虎女岂配犬子。将诸葛瑾赶出账外。吴侯大怒，埋怨下官当初不该作保。\n为此，下官定下了一计，不用一枪一刀，管保荆州唾手而得。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大夫定了何计？老夫倒要领教。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在宜阳江中，摆下酒宴大会。舱内埋伏甲兵，请云长过江赴宴，酒席宴前讨取\n荆州。他还了扁罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他若不还呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他若不还，金钟为号，钟声一响，伏兵齐起，生擒关羽。哪怕他不还荆州！"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此计可是大夫所定？"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是下官所定。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "择于几时？"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "本月十三日接他前来，荆州岂不是唾手而得？"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住，那孔明先生可在荆州？"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孔明若在荆州，下官我也不敢造次！"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好计，好计。酒席宴前何人陪宴？"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "少不得下官陪宴。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是你陪宴？"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "太尉为何发笑？"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "非是老朽发笑，我笑只笑大夫你，好藐视关羽也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "非是老朽微微笑，\n堪羡关羽有略韬。\n谁人不知是英豪？\n万般无奈暂降曹。\n上马金下马银赐过锦袍。\n夜读春秋一通宵。\n挂印封金不取分毫。\n酒祭青龙火焰飘。\n不中曹瞒计笼牢。\n难瞒孔明妙算高。\n水底捞月枉费劳！"
        },
        {
          "character": "屯兵聚义把贼扫、失徐州被困土山道、三日宴来五日醪、美女十人他不要、后来写下辞曹表、那曹操霸陵桥边备醇醪、独行千里保皇嫂、你把关羽轻视了、大夫今把荆州讨、鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "下官定的此计，神鬼难测，谅关羽难以知晓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孔明可知？"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孔明若在此，下官也不能定下此计。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谅你也不能哪。老朽倒有一计。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有何妙计？"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请问大夫，河下船只可多？"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "战船多得很，要它何用？"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你把战船三十只一连，五十号一连，都把它连将起来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那岂不是送关羽的归路么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不是关羽归路，是大夫的生路哇！"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "船上安排连环套，\n江边搭起一浮桥。\n你好走来你也好逃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "倘若关羽行霸道、鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "两旁都是我国将士，谅他插翅难飞！"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老朽还有一计。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "又有什么计策？"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你回去备下三牲祭礼，掀开你家祖先堂，祭过你的祖先；再备精美的酒席一桌，\n与你令正夫人吃上几杯分别酒哇！"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吃饱了会上怎生动手？"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪还容得你动手哇！"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宜阳江上把荆州讨，\n酒席宴前惹祸苗。\n做一个饱鬼赴阴曹。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒要多吃饭要饱、鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "下官此来，非求计而来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到此作甚？"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请太尉前去陪宴。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "陪宴何不早讲？请！"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（乔玄作闪腰。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喔唷唷！"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "太尉怎么样了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "与大夫施礼，闪了我的腰了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪是闪了腰，分明是怕关羽的刀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "偃月刀我却不怕。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你怕作么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我怕关羽身后一员虎将。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他叫什么名字？"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "名叫周仓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，无名小卒，怕他作甚？"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你道周仓无名小卒，老朽单单怕那一个呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怕他何来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你道周仓无名小，\n他是将中一英豪。\n双手惯用紫金镖。\n酒席宴前惹祸苗。\n劈头就是那一刀。\n不把性命换酒肴。\n闷来书房把琴操。\n学一个忙里偷闲、自在逍遥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "两军阵前烟尘扫、此番会上他必到、大夫一言讲差了、老朽年迈七十了、闲来亭园观花草、闲事闲非不问好、鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "太尉既不肯前去，下官告辞了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老朽相送！"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "逢君一席话，"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "胜读十年书。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃、乔玄",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（鲁肃行。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大夫请转！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（鲁肃复回。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "太尉唤回，有何话讲？"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我有几句话你要牢牢谨记。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "太尉请吩咐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大夫哇！"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "昔日张良品玉箫，\n赤胆忠心保汉朝。\n一统山河爵禄高。\n得饶人来把人饶。\n关羽智略比你高，枉费徒劳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔玄",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（乔玄下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "指望乔府领高教，"
        }
      ],
